snippet.title: Open Beta Trailer | HAWKED
snippet.description:
HAWKED is ready for Open Beta on PC, and this time it’s a total free for all. Board the Riftwake and explore, fight, and loot your way across X-Isle from August 3–17: https://playhawked.com

HAWKED is a free online PvPvE extraction shooter coming to Windows PC and consoles. Squad up with pals to explore a mysterious island and battle monsters, solve puzzles, outfox enemies, and escape with ancient treasures!

#HAWKED #PLAYHAWKED #RENEGADE

Check out more HAWKED videos on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@playHAWKED

Follow HAWKED:

Official Website: https://playhawked.com

✅ Discord: https://discord.gg/hawked

✅ Twitter/X: https://twitter.com/PlayHAWKED

✅ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HAWKEDGame/

✅ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playhawked/
